# production-url-smoke.allowlist
#
# Routes listed here are KNOWN to 404 in production for a documented reason.
# This is not a place to silence new bugs — every entry needs a "why" comment.
# If you add a route here, also list it in the RC report's "未做（明确边界）"
# section. Prune entries as soon as the route ships.
#
# Format: one route per line (must start with `/`). Lines starting with `#`
# and blank lines are ignored.

# /me — directory exists locally as a parent for /me/matters and
# /me/consultations but has no page.tsx of its own, so production 404s
# the bare `/me`. Pending product decision on whether `/me` should redirect
# to `/me/matters` or render a hub page. Tracked in
# docs/ops/TEBIQ_1_0_RC_SPRINT_REPORT_2026-05-17.md §3.
/me

# /sample-package — page.tsx exists locally on rc-polish/q1-q5 but has not
# yet been deployed to production. Remove this entry after first production
# deploy that includes app/sample-package/page.tsx.
/sample-package
